---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="How to Play">
  <section>
    <h2>📖 How to Play Party Pocket</h2>
    <p class="lead">Learn how to host games, invite friends, and dominate the leaderboards!</p>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Getting Started</h3>
      <p>Party Pocket is designed for easy, quick setup:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>✅ <strong>One player acts as the host</strong> — They start a game room</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Other players join as guests</strong> — Using QR code or room code</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>All phones must be on the same WiFi network</strong> — No internet required!</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Games are peer-to-peer</strong> — No servers involved</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>🎮 Hosting a Game</h3>
      <p class="lead"><strong>Step 1: Open the App</strong></p>
      <p>Launch Party Pocket on your phone. You'll see the home screen with options to Host or Join.</p>

      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px"><strong>Step 2: Select "Host Game"</strong></p>
      <p>Tap the "Host" button. You'll be asked to enter a room name and select which games to play.</p>

      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px"><strong>Step 3: Share the Connection</strong></p>
      <p>Once you're hosting, you'll see:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>A <strong>QR code</strong> that others can scan with their cameras or the app</li>
        <li>A <strong>room code</strong> (like "PARTY123") that guests can type in manually</li>
        <li>The <strong>number of players</strong> currently connected</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px"><strong>Step 4: Start Playing</strong></p>
      <p>Once 2-8 players have joined, tap "Start Game" to begin. Each game will play in sequence.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>👥 Joining a Game</h3>
      <p class="lead"><strong>Step 1: Open the App</strong></p>
      <p>Launch Party Pocket and select "Join Game".</p>

      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px"><strong>Step 2: Scan or Enter Code</strong></p>
      <p>You have two options:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Scan QR Code:</strong> Tap the camera icon and scan the host's QR code</li>
        <li><strong>Enter Room Code:</strong> Manually type in the room code (e.g., "PARTY123")</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px"><strong>Step 3: Confirm Your Name</strong></p>
      <p>Enter your player name (e.g., "Alex", "Chris"). This will be shown on the leaderboard.</p>

      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px"><strong>Step 4: Wait for Host to Start</strong></p>
      <p>You're connected! Wait for the host to start the game. You'll see other players joining in real-time.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>🎯 Gameplay & Rounds</h3>
      <p class="lead"><strong>Before Each Game</strong></p>
      <p>You'll see a countdown timer and instructions for the current game. Read the rules—they differ for each game!</p>

      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px"><strong>During Each Game</strong></p>
      <p>Your phone will vibrate or show visual cues to let you know when to tap, tilt, or hold steady. Check the screen—every second counts!</p>

      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px"><strong>After Each Game</strong></p>
      <p>Results appear instantly with a leaderboard showing:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your rank (1st, 2nd, etc.)</li>
        <li>Your score for that game</li>
        <li>All players' scores in order</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top:16px">You'll have time to celebrate or prepare for the next game!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>🏆 Winning & Scoring</h3>
      <p class="lead"><strong>Game-by-Game Scoring</strong></p>
      <p>Each game awards points based on performance:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>🥇 <strong>1st Place:</strong> Highest points</li>
        <li>🥈 <strong>2nd Place:</strong> Medium points</li>
        <li>🥉 <strong>3rd Place & Below:</strong> Fewer points</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px"><strong>Overall Winner</strong></p>
      <p>After all selected games are played, the player with the most total points wins! A final leaderboard will crown the champion and show the final standings.</p>

      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px"><strong>Ties</strong></p>
      <p>If two players tie in total points, a sudden-death tiebreaker game determines the winner.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>💡 Pro Tips</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Stable WiFi:</strong> Make sure all players are on a strong WiFi connection. Move away from interference if games lag.</li>
        <li><strong>Clear Space:</strong> For Tilt Racer and Hold Steady, have a stable surface to play on.</li>
        <li><strong>Phone Orientation:</strong> Some games require different phone orientations. Pay attention to the on-screen instructions!</li>
        <li><strong>Fast Fingers:</strong> For Tap Frenzy, use both thumbs and tap rapidly. The faster you tap, the better!</li>
        <li><strong>Focus & React:</strong> For Reaction Roulette, stay focused and anticipate the color change. Reaction time is key.</li>
        <li><strong>Steady Hand:</strong> For Hold Steady, rest on a table or hold very still. Even small movements count!</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>❓ Common Questions</h3>
      <p class="lead"><strong>Q: Do I need an internet connection?</strong></p>
      <p>A: No! Party Pocket works completely on local WiFi. Perfect for events with spotty internet.</p>

      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px"><strong>Q: Can I play with more than 8 players?</strong></p>
      <p>A: The app is optimized for 2-8 players. More players may cause lag or connection issues.</p>

      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px"><strong>Q: What phones are supported?</strong></p>
      <p>A: Android 8.0 and higher. iOS support coming soon!</p>

      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px"><strong>Q: Can I host on my laptop or PC?</strong></p>
      <p>A: Currently, the host must be an Android device. Guests can only be Android devices.</p>

      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px"><strong>Q: What if someone's phone disconnects mid-game?</strong></p>
      <p>A: They're automatically removed from that game. If the host disconnects, the game ends.</p>

      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px"><strong>Q: Can I change the games after starting?</strong></p>
      <p>A: No, the game list is locked once the host starts. Plan ahead and select the games you want!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>🎉 Ready to Host?</h3>
      <p class="lead">Download the app and start hosting epic party gaming sessions with your friends!</p>
      <p><a href="/install" style="color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none">Go to Install Guide →</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .lead {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
